data.description: Welcome to this magnificent 7-bedroom, 5-bathroom home nestled in sought after Jacobs Farm Subdivision. With 5044 square feet of living space, this exquisite residence is a haven of sophistication. The beautifully landscaped front yard leads you to a grand entrance, setting the tone for the rest of the house. Step inside and you are immediately greeted by the charm of a beautiful 2 story foyer and open floor plan. The main floor boasts a stunning formal living room/office, a gracious dining area, and a cozy family room. With 10-foot ceilings, the home exudes an airy and grand ambiance, creating an inviting and warm atmosphere. The kitchen, is a chef's dream with pristine cabinets ensuring that meal preparation is a delight.  The oversized master bedroom is a true retreat with a sitting area and spa-like en-suite bathroom is an oasis.  Complete with a double vanity, and all the amenities needed for a pampering experience. Each of the secondary bedrooms are generously sized and carefully positioned to ensure privacy and comfort. The top floor loft offers space for entertaining, a movie room, or in home gym. This exceptional property combines the best of indoor and outdoor living, making it an ideal choice for those seeking a harmonious blend of luxury, comfort, and entertainment. Located in a excellent school district, convenient access to shopping and dining, and easy connectivity to major transportation routes.  Don't miss the opportunity to call this property home!
